==============di er hua
zai zhe ge shi jie che hao xiang shi yi zhong biao zhi che de hao huai jue ding ni de she hui di wei

zai meng li wo shi  ge ji xie shi, wo de lao ban he yi ge tong shi kai che dao wo de zhu suo lai ping yong wo , jing guo yi fan zhou xuan
wo zui zhong tong yi le . wo gen zhe ta men xia lou ,tong shi dai wo men qu kai chi ,zhe ge shi hou tu ran chu xian yi dui re shi de xiao nian
qing, nv de hen bi shi wo men ,nan de xiang yao xiu ta na bu zhi ming de pao che ,zai wo men chu ku de shi hou nan de  bu zhi dao an le che shang
de shen me an niu .che de lun tai bian le yi xia xing zhuang .jiu wang men che de wei zhi kao le yi xia .shuo -ni men gan pen dao jiu pei si ni
men. yin wei tai jin ,wo men mei fa chu qu .tong shi hen bu gao  xing ,lao ban hen wei qu jin hu ai qiu de mu guang kan zhe dui fang .wo  jiu he
dui fang shuo - qie you shen liao bu qi de lao zi you lan bo ji ni dou mei you chu lai de se . dui fang bu xiang xin   ,wo shuo  ni men deng zhe
yu shi wo wang yi dong lou de lou ding chuan ,wo shuo wo de fang zai lou ding ting che chang.wo chuan dao lou ding kan ta men ye gen le shang lai ,wo ji zhong sheng zhi
zai lou shang wo bing mei you shou huo ,xiang zhe xian shan ren ,zhao le ling wai de  lou dao feng kuang chuan xing xia qu mei xiang dao na ge nan de
mao si fa xian wo de yi tu.yi gen zhe xia lai . xiang yong che du zhu wo de chu lu ,mei xiang dao zhe ge shi hou cong di di xia chuan chu yi ge lan bo ji ni
,xiao nian qing men kan sha le ,li ma liu zou le .lao ban ye mu deng kou dai ,qie sheng sheng de guo lai. ran hou wo xian shi yi fan xiang shou ,ran hou
guan diao yao kong ,lan bo ji ni bian chen le yi ge tuo la jia ¬haha¬ yuan lai wo zai di xia che ku tu ran fa xian wo you ge ceng jing shi yong de bian xing bi
